title: Angels - Their Finest Hour And Then Some (2008) [FLAC]
description:
Band: The Angels
Album: Their Finest Hour And Then Some
Year: 2008
Country: Australia
Genre: Hard Rock

2008 digitally remastered and expanded edition of this collection from Australia's premier Hard Rockers featuring bonus tracks. The Angels were briefly known as Angel City in the U.S. Includes all of the band's biggest hits and finest tracks including one new track and 'Who Rings The Bell', a hit that has never been on any studio album! 19 tracks.
